Package main.java.com.nutrisci.dao

Class InMemoryNutritionDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.com.nutrisci.dao.InMemoryNutritionDAO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NutritionDAO
    public class InMemoryNutritionDAO
extends java.lang.Object
implements NutritionDAO
    In-memory implementation of NutritionDAO for retrieving nutritional information. This class uses a hardcoded cache to simulate a database of food items and their calorie and nutrient breakdowns.

        public double getCaloriesPerGram​(java.lang.String foodName)
        Returns the calorie count per gram for a given food item. Falls back to a default rate of 1.0 kcal/gram if the food is unrecognized.
        Specified by:

        Parameters:

      • getNutrientBreakdownPerGram

        public java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​java.lang.Double> getNutrientBreakdownPerGram​(java.lang.String foodName)
        Returns a map of nutrient breakdown per gram for a given food item. Currently, this is a stub implementation that only returns calories.
        Specified by:
        getNutrientBreakdownPerGram in interface NutritionDAO
        Parameters:
        foodName - The name of the food item.
        Returns:
